<div class="bulk-format-card card mb-6 sm:mb-8">
    <div class="bulk-format-header">
        <h2 class="bulk-format-title">
            {% include 'components/ui/icon.twig' with { name: 'ri-information-line', class: 'text-gold-600' } %}
            Format yang didukung
        </h2>
        <a href="/participants/bulk/template" class="btn-secondary bulk-format-download">
            {% include 'components/ui/icon.twig' with { name: 'ri-download-2-line', class: 'mr-1.5', size: 'sm' } %}
            Unduh Template CSV
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="bulk-format-body">
        <p class="bulk-format-intro">
            Kolom lengkap (disarankan): <strong>Nama, Rank, Gender, Telepon, GMS</strong>.
            Paste dari Excel/Google Sheets (tab otomatis) atau upload file CSV.
            Kolom Gender, Telepon, dan GMS boleh dikosongkan.
        </p>

        <ul class="bulk-format-list">
            <li><strong>Header otomatis</strong> — baris pertama <code>Nama,Rank,Gender,Telepon,GMS</code> dikenali & dilewati</li>
            <li><strong>Format singkat</strong> — <code>Calvin,C</code> (rank wajib; gender/telp/GMS opsional)</li>
            <li><strong>No + Nama + Rank</strong> — <code>1,Calvin,C</code> (kolom nomor opsional)</li>
            <li><strong>Duplikat</strong> — nama yang sudah ada di daftar global (atau sudah di session) otomatis dilewati</li>
        </ul>

        <pre class="bulk-format-example">Nama,Rank,Gender,Telepon,GMS
Calvin,C,Male,081234567890,GMS
Yosua,B+,Female,081298765432,VIP
Pat,B,Male,,CP
Kevin,A-,Male,08111222333,PURI</pre>

        <div class="bulk-format-ref">
            <p class="bulk-format-ref-heading">Nilai yang valid</p>
            <div class="bulk-format-ref-grid">
                <div class="bulk-format-ref-item">
                    <p class="bulk-format-ref-label">Rank</p>
                    <div class="bulk-format-chips">
                        {% for value in ranks|keys %}
                            <span class="bulk-format-chip bulk-format-chip-rank">{{ value }}</span>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bulk-format-ref-item">
                    <p class="bulk-format-ref-label">Gender</p>
                    <div class="bulk-format-chips">
                        {% for value, label in genders %}
                            <span class="bulk-format-chip">{{ label }}</span>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    <p class="bulk-format-ref-hint">Juga diterima: M, F, Pria, Wanita</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bulk-format-ref-item">
                    <p class="bulk-format-ref-label">GMS</p>
                    <div class="bulk-format-chips">
                        {% for value in gmsSources|keys %}
                            <span class="bulk-format-chip bulk-format-chip-gms bulk-format-chip-{{ value|lower }}">{{ value }}</span>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
